            <!-- FAQ List -->
            <div id="faqList">
                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="tailoring">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>How long does bespoke tailoring take?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Bespoke tailoring typically takes <strong>10-21 business days</strong> depending on
                            complexity and current workload. Premium and Concierge tier orders receive priority
                            processing. You'll receive a detailed timeline during your consultation with estimated
                            completion dates for each stage: measurement → fabric cutting → stitching → embroidery →
                            fitting → delivery.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="tailoring">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Can I make changes after placing a tailoring order?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Minor adjustments can be made <strong>within 48 hours</strong> of placing your order at no
                            additional cost. Significant design changes after production has begun may incur additional
                            costs and extend the delivery timeline. Contact your tailor immediately through your
                            dashboard if you need to make changes.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="tailoring">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>What's the difference between your service tiers?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            <strong>Essential (₦95,000):</strong> Standard measurement, basic fabric selection, 1
                            fitting session, 2-week turnaround.<br /><br />
                            <strong>Premium (₦195,000):</strong> Precision 3D measurement, premium fabric consultation,
                            2 fitting sessions, 10-day turnaround, embroidery options.<br /><br />
                            <strong>Concierge (₦495,000):</strong> Home visit measurement, exclusive fabric sourcing,
                            unlimited fittings, 5-day priority turnaround, custom embroidery & beading, personal
                            stylist.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="tailoring">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Do you offer alterations on existing garments?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Yes! We provide <strong>alteration services</strong> for existing garments including hem
                            adjustments, waist take-in/let-out, sleeve shortening, and more. Pricing depends on the
                            complexity of the alteration. Bring your garment to any of our studios for a complimentary
                            assessment and quote.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="measurements">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>How do I provide my measurements?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            You can provide measurements in three convenient ways:<br /><br />
                            <strong>1. In-Studio:</strong> Visit our Lagos or Abuja studio for professional in-person
                            measurement by our master tailors — free with any tailoring order.<br />
                            <strong>2. Virtual Consultation:</strong> Schedule a video call where we guide you through
                            the measurement process step by step.<br />
                            <strong>3. Self-Measurement:</strong> Enter your measurements manually in your account
                            profile using our interactive measurement guide with visual body references.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="measurements">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>What if my measurements are incorrect?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            We strongly recommend professional measurement for the best fit. If you provide
                            self-measurements that result in an ill-fitting garment, we offer
                            <strong>one complimentary adjustment</strong>. Additional alterations may be charged at
                            standard rates. Our master tailors review all measurements before production and will flag
                            any potential issues.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="measurements">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>How often should I update my measurements?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            We recommend updating your measurement profile <strong>every 6 months</strong> or whenever
                            you experience significant weight changes. You can update your measurements anytime from
                            your account dashboard. For the most accurate fit, we recommend a professional fitting at
                            least once per year.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="orders">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>What payment methods do you accept?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            We accept all major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express),
                            <strong>bank transfers</strong>, and <strong>mobile money payments</strong>. For bespoke
                            orders over ₦500,000, a 50% deposit is required to begin work, with the balance due upon
                            completion and before delivery.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="orders">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Can I cancel my order?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            <strong>Ready-to-wear orders</strong> can be cancelled within 24 hours for a full refund.
                            <strong>Bespoke tailoring orders:</strong> deposits are non-refundable once production has
                            begun. Contact our support team immediately if you need to cancel — we'll work with you to
                            find the best solution.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="orders">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Is there a minimum order for fabrics?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Yes, most fabrics have a <strong>minimum order of 3 yards</strong>. This ensures you have
                            enough material for a complete garment with proper pattern matching. For specific projects,
                            our tailors can advise on the exact yardage needed during your consultation.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="shipping">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Do you ship internationally?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Yes! We ship to <strong>over 30 countries</strong> worldwide including the United States,
                            United Kingdom, Canada, Ghana, South Africa, and across the European Union. International
                            shipping rates are calculated at checkout. Customers are responsible for any customs duties,
                            taxes, or import fees imposed by their country.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="shipping">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>How can I track my order?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Once your order ships, you'll receive an <strong>email with a tracking number</strong>. You
                            can also track your order status in real-time from your account dashboard under "My Orders."
                            For tailoring orders, you can monitor progress through each stage of production — from
                            fabric cutting to final fitting.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="shipping">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Is shipping free?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            <strong>Store pickup is always free</strong> at our Lagos and Abuja studios. Home delivery
                            within Lagos costs ₦5,000, and Abuja delivery is ₦10,000. <strong>Free shipping</strong> on
                            all orders over ₦200,000 within Nigeria. International shipping rates vary by destination.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="fabrics">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Can I request fabric samples?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Absolutely! We offer <strong>complimentary fabric swatches</strong> for most of our
                            collection. You can request up to 5 swatches per order through our fabric page. Swatches
                            typically arrive within 5-7 business days so you can feel the texture and see the true color
                            before purchasing.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="fabrics">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Where do your fabrics come from?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Our fabrics are sourced from <strong>premium suppliers</strong> globally:<br /><br />
                            <strong>Nigeria:</strong> Aso Oke, Adire, and traditional handwoven textiles<br />
                            <strong>Italy:</strong> Damask, silk, and luxury brocade<br />
                            <strong>Turkey:</strong> Premium cotton blends and linen<br /><br />
                            We personally vet all suppliers to ensure quality, ethical production, and authentic
                            materials.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="fabrics">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>How do I care for my fabric?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Care instructions vary by fabric type. Generally:<br /><br />
                            <strong>Aso Oke & Brocade:</strong> Dry clean only<br />
                            <strong>Cotton blends:</strong> Machine wash cold, gentle cycle<br />
                            <strong>Silk:</strong> Dry clean only<br />
                            <strong>Damask:</strong> Dry clean recommended<br /><br />
                            Specific care instructions are included with every fabric purchase and on the product page.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="account">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>How do I create an account?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Creating an account is <strong>simple and free</strong>. Click "Sign In" then "Create
                            Account." You'll need your phone number (which serves as your username), email address, and
                            a password. Once registered, you can save measurements, track orders, manage your profile,
                            and access exclusive features.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="account">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Is my personal information secure?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Absolutely. We use <strong>industry-standard encryption</strong> to protect all personal and
                            payment information. Your measurement data is stored securely and never shared with third
                            parties. You can request deletion of your data at any time by contacting our privacy team.
                            See our Privacy Policy for full details.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" data-cat="account">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>I forgot my password. What do I do?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>
                            Click "Forgot password?" on the login page. Enter your registered phone number and we'll
                            send a <strong>password reset link</strong> via SMS and email. Follow the link to create a
                            new password. For security, reset links expire after 30 minutes.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
